{"word":"Laver","slug":"laver","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Laver</b> Directions for making<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=20'>Exo 30:20</a><br/> Situation of, in the tabernacle, tent of the congregation, and the altar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=7'>Exo 40:7</a><br/> Sanctified<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=28'>Exo 30:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=11'>Exo 40:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=11'>Lev 8:11</a><br/> Used for washing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=32'>Exo 40:32</a><br/> Brazen, made by Solomon for the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=26'>1Ki 7:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=30'>1Ki 7:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=39'>1Ki 7:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=14'>2Ch 4:14</a><br/> Altered by Ahaz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=17'>2Ki 16:17</a><br/> Broken and carried to Babylon by the Chaldeans<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=13'>2Ki 25:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=16'>2Ki 25:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=17'>Jer 52:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=20'>Jer 52:20</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=4&verse=6'>Rev 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=15&verse=2'>Rev 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=8'>Exo 38:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=23'>1